    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently runs roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior shows several dents, rusted panels, and fading paint, and the interior has seen heavy use with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or could serve as a source for parts.",
